Package api.equinix.javasdk.networkedge.enums

package api.equinix.javasdk.networkedge.enums
Network Edge enumerations for the Equinix Java SDK. Defines typed constants for device types, device statuses, license types, management types, package codes, connectivity options, BGP peering states, VPN statuses, ACL template statuses, and other Network Edge domain values used throughout the device provisioning and management lifecycle.
